<PrivacyLayout appSlug="randomizer" lastUpdated="2026-05-17">

  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <p>Randomizer is a free utility app. It collects nothing personal. It shows ads served by Google AdMob, which has its own privacy practices.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Nothing personal.</strong> No account, no email, no login.</li>
    <li><strong>AdMob (Google):</strong> serves ads and may collect device identifiers for ad personalization, governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's privacy policy</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No analytics SDKs beyond what AdMob provides.</li>
    <li>No selling or sharing of personal data with other third parties.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>You can opt out of personalized ads via your device's ad settings (Android: Settings → Google → Ads).</p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>Randomizer is not directed at children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p><a href="mailto:hello@brooo.app">hello@brooo.app</a></p>

</PrivacyLayout>
